<h2>TfL Customer Services</h2>

<p>Contact Customer Services for all ticket enquiries including Oyster and contactless payment, travel information queries and journey planning on all methods of transport including roads. We can also help with lost property and complaints.</p>

<p><a href="https://custserv.tfl.gov.uk/icss_csip/SolutionDatabaseStart.do?nav=askQ">Search common questions or contact us online</a></p>

<p><strong>Phone: </strong>0343 222 1234*</p>

<p>You can reach all the departments below on this number but please note their opening hours:</p>

<p><strong>Travel Information and Journey Planning enquiries for all modes</strong> (24 hours)<br />
