<h3>Automated Journey Planner</h3>

<p>Our Customer Services number also offers an automated service for A-to-B journeys. Just give the start and end point of any journey, and it will give you the quickest route. It can even text the journey details to your mobile phone.</p>

<p>This automated service works for:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Stations</li>
	<li>Hospitals</li>
	<li>Postcodes</li>
	<li>Points of interest and major landmarks</li>
</ul>

<p>If your journey is complicated, involves multiple locations or you have special requirements, you can still speak to one of our travel advisers.</p>

<p>If you request a text message, the average journey will usually be sent within a single message, however more complex journeys may take up to a maximum of two messages, charged at the price of a standard rate message.</p>

